1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:02,560
前情提要
Previously on The Mob Doctor...

2
00:00:02,600 --> 00:00:04,618
只要你还在芝加哥，你就欠我的，一言为定
<i>As long as you're in Chicago,I own you. That's the deal.</i>

3
00:00:04,652 --> 00:00:07,270
我听说你想接手莫拉提的生意
So, I hear you want to take over Moretti's deal with us.

4
00:00:07,288 --> 00:00:08,438
对，没错
Yeah, that's right.

5
00:00:08,456 --> 00:00:09,606
不可能
Ain't gonna happen.

6
00:00:09,624 --> 00:00:11,158
我知道怎么两头拿钱
I know about the double dipping.

7
00:00:11,209 --> 00:00:13,794
我们从艾尔的投币机生意中抽25%
<i>Our cut's 25% al on the machines.</i>

8
00:00:13,828 --> 00:00:15,712
你就想要15%
You were asking for 15%.

9
00:00:15,747 --> 00:00:17,247
我的兄弟们不会答应的
My brother's not gonna like this.

10
00:00:18,082 --> 00:00:20,384
赛莱斯特，康斯坦汀
Celeste.Constantine.

11
00:00:20,418 --> 00:00:22,285
你真觉得联合财团是个好主意吗？
You really think uniting the syndicate is a good thing?

12
00:00:22,303 --> 00:00:24,504
是的，这是个潘多拉魔盒
I do.It's a Pandora's Box.

13
00:00:24,555 --> 00:00:26,306
开会吧
Let's get this meeting started.

14
00:00:26,341 --> 00:00:27,391
你要是不小心点
And if you're not careful,

15
00:00:27,425 --> 00:00:29,292
你就又得蹲监狱，或者更糟
You'll end up back in jail --or worse.

16
00:00:29,310 --> 00:00:31,678
康斯坦丁来了，你得赶紧走
Constantine's coming.You have to leave.

17
00:00:31,729 --> 00:00:33,647
听我说，我刚回到你身边，不想现在就走
Listen to me. I just got you back.
There's no way I'm running now.

18
00:00:33,681 --> 00:00:36,016
没有别的办法，你现在必须得走了
There is no other way.
You have to go -- now.

19
00:00:47,144 --> 00:00:50,797
真的，没事，你尝尝
Look -- I don't care.Take a bite.

20
00:00:50,831 --> 00:00:54,550
吃吧，巧克力吃起来感觉不怎么样
Go on. Take a bite.The chocolate tastes cheap.

21
00:00:54,585 --> 00:00:57,470
我不想在我的潘趣卷里放便宜巧克力
I-I-I don't want to have cheap
chocolate on my punsch rolls.

22
00:00:57,504 --> 00:01:00,423
斯塔沃斯，过来帮我尝尝这个
Stavos. Come over here and taste something for me.

23
00:01:06,847 --> 00:01:08,164
挺好吃的
Tastes good.

24
00:01:08,198 --> 00:01:10,850
我想要的是芝加哥最好的潘趣卷
I want the best-tasting damn punsch rolls in Chicago.

25
00:01:10,884 --> 00:01:14,520
多花点钱用比利时黑巧克力做
Spend the extra buck and get the belgian dark.

26
00:01:14,571 --> 00:01:16,672
你知道蛋糕店只是个掩护吗？
The bakery's just a front,you know?

27
00:01:16,707 --> 00:01:19,025
这是用来洗钱的是吗？
Cash business to launder our money, right?

28
00:01:19,076 --> 00:01:20,193
我父亲曾经说过
Like my old man said,

29
00:01:20,244 --> 00:01:22,495
如果你想做事，就得把事情做好
If you're gonna do something,do it right.

30
00:01:22,529 --> 00:01:24,780
说到把事情做好
Speaking of doing things right,

31
00:01:24,815 --> 00:01:28,518
阿马特斯的游戏机保护费又交晚了
The Amatos are late with their gaming-machines cut again.

32
00:01:28,552 --> 00:01:31,003
你给泰塔斯打电话
You call Titus.

33
00:01:31,038 --> 00:01:33,322
告诉他每晚交一天我就多收一个百分点
You tell him I'm gonna take a point for every day he's late.

34
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:35,991
你有客人来了
looks like you have a visitor.

35
00:01:39,379 --> 00:01:40,847
小赛
Celeste.

36
00:01:40,881 --> 00:01:45,101
郊区的生意你要给特拉帕尼50%的抽成
You're giving Trapani 50% of our downtown action.

37
00:01:45,135 --> 00:01:47,836
对呀，你承诺给我的也是50%
<i>That's right.You promised me 50%.</i>

38
00:01:47,855 --> 00:01:49,505
对呀
Also right.

39
00:01:49,523 --> 00:01:50,723
你把所有的钱都给我们了
So, if you're giving away all the money,

40
00:01:50,774 --> 00:01:51,858
你自己还剩下什么呀？
Then what's left for you?

41
00:01:51,892 --> 00:01:54,610
嘿，我给弄杯咖啡或者小蛋糕吧？
Hey, can I get you an espresso or a cupcake?

42
00:01:54,645 --> 00:01:57,029
这儿的潘趣卷做得一般
I don't recommend the punsch rolls.

43
00:01:57,064 --> 00:01:59,115
你给我解释解释
I'd like an explanation,Constantine.

44
00:01:59,149 --> 00:02:00,449
哦
Oh.

45
00:02:01,518 --> 00:02:03,185
嘿，哥儿几个，你们先出去一下
Hey, fellas,give me a couple minutes.

46
00:02:06,073 --> 00:02:10,059
西城和北城的生意都拿50%
The West Side and the North Side are both gonna get 50%.

47
00:02:10,093 --> 00:02:11,377
我一向说话算数
I always keep my word.

48
00:02:11,411 --> 00:02:14,113
那南城就什么都没有吗？你什么也不拿？
<i>And the South Side gets nothing? You get nothing?</i>

49
00:02:14,147 --> 00:02:16,499
接管了郊区的生意
Well, you know,taking over downtown

50
00:02:16,533 --> 00:02:18,751
我收获的可不仅仅是钱
Means a lot more to me than money.

51
00:02:18,802 --> 00:02:20,720
你觉着我能信你这话吗？
you expect me to believe that?

52
00:02:20,754 --> 00:02:24,039
艾尔・卡彭来之后就一直没弄完
Well, it hasn't been done since Al Capone.

53
00:02:25,676 --> 00:02:27,310
你太自负了吧
So, this is about your ego.

54
00:02:27,344 --> 00:02:29,979
随便你怎么说
You call it what you want.

55
00:02:30,013 --> 00:02:32,481
对我来说，这就是在创造历史
To me,it's about making history.

56
00:02:32,516 --> 00:02:36,152
咱们把这个盒子打开
Hey, what do you say...We crack this box open,

57
00:02:36,186 --> 00:02:39,388
喝点儿香槟酒，你帮我拿点冰块来怎么样？
We put this nice champagne you gave me on ice.

58
00:02:39,406 --> 00:02:40,539
啊？
What?

59
00:02:40,574 --> 00:02:42,975
你今儿早上送我的香槟啊
The bottle of champagne you sent me this morning.

60
00:02:43,010 --> 00:02:46,395
老康，我没给你送过香槟
Tino, I didn't send that to you.

61
00:02:48,298 --> 00:02:50,383
那是谁送的？
Then who did?

62
00:02:52,619 --> 00:02:56,405
你干吗呀？
What are you doing?

63
00:02:56,423 --> 00:02:58,190
这里边装了一个压板
It's rigged with a pressure plate.

64
00:03:04,798 --> 00:03:07,750
在这儿呢
Here we go.

65
00:03:19,313 --> 00:03:22,898
你最好出去等一会
You better wait outside.

66
00:03:27,621 --> 00:03:30,039
家庭作业――用超声波
Take-home message --use the ultrasound

67
00:03:30,073 --> 00:03:32,208
预测病人体内的脓液流动状态
To estimate fluid status in septic patients

68
00:03:32,242 --> 00:03:36,545
观察呼吸以判断下静脉腔是否破裂
By looking at the IVC collapse with respiration.

69
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:41,317
最后一个作业，患者满意度调查
And one last thing --patient-satisfaction surveys.

70
00:03:41,351 --> 00:03:43,052
伯德做得很认真
Board takes them seriously.

71
00:03:43,086 --> 00:03:47,006
我建议你们也认真对待
I suggest that you do, too.

72
00:03:47,057 --> 00:03:49,342
喂？你讲义的第三页
Hello? Page three of your handouts,

73
00:03:49,393 --> 00:03:52,178
有新的规定，今天就要落实
You find a new script being implemented today.

74
00:03:52,229 --> 00:03:53,295
鲁滨逊大夫
Dr. Robinson.

75
00:03:56,817 --> 00:03:59,852
你好，我是布兰克医生
"hello,my name is Dr. Blank.

76
00:03:59,903 --> 00:04:01,570
这是我的名片
"here's my card.

77
00:04:01,605 --> 00:04:05,057
抱歉让你久等了，布兰克马上就来
I am sorry you had to wait blank minutes to see me."

78
00:04:05,092 --> 00:04:08,194
我再给你拿个枕头或者被子吧？
"can I offer you an extra pillow or blanket?"

79
00:04:09,913 --> 00:04:11,914
我们是医生还是服务员？
Are we surgeons or room service?

80
00:04:11,948 --> 00:04:14,417
每个医生都要接受
Any doctor receiving three failing grades

81
00:04:14,451 --> 00:04:16,502
一个月三次的医患态度检查
Within a month will be attending
the bedside-manner seminar.

82
00:04:16,536 --> 00:04:18,371
好，我这就来
All right, on my way.

83
00:04:18,422 --> 00:04:20,823
急诊室五分钟之后要来一个特重病人
We got a V.I.P.Five minutes out from the E.R.

84
00:04:20,841 --> 00:04:22,208
今天谁值班？我
Who's on trauma call? I am.

85
00:04:22,259 --> 00:04:23,676
好吧，你跟我来，鲁滨逊，你也来
All right, you're with me.Dr. Robinson, you, too.

86
00:04:23,710 --> 00:04:25,845
我已经被安排在术后检查门诊了
I'm scheduled for post-op clinic.

87
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:28,014
你被抽调了，已经通知前台广播了
Not anymore.The paramedics radioed ahead.

88
00:04:28,048 --> 00:04:29,715
病人点名让你来治疗
The patient requested you by name.

89
00:04:29,766 --> 00:04:31,934
是谁呀？咱们会知道的
Who's the patient? We're about to find out.

90
00:04:31,968 --> 00:04:34,603
自行车事故，28岁，男性
cycling accident. 28-year-old male.

91
00:04:34,638 --> 00:04:37,440
头部损伤导致神志不清
Head injury with altered mental status.

92
00:04:37,474 --> 00:04:39,775
右手腕部骨折，急性知觉丧失
Open right wrist fracture A.L.O.C.（Acute Loss of Consciousness） 

93
00:04:39,810 --> 00:04:41,777
气象色谱标准10，体征稳定
GCS 10.Vitals stable.

94
00:04:41,812 --> 00:04:43,779
胸前端和手足损伤
Abrasions to anterior chest and extremities.

95
00:04:43,814 --> 00:04:44,780
这是谁呀？
Who is he?

96
00:04:44,815 --> 00:04:46,782
杰克・汉森――联邦检察官的儿子
Jack Hanson --U.S. Attorney's son.

97
00:04:46,817 --> 00:04:48,768
他为什么点名让你治疗？你认识他？
Why would he ask for you? You know him?

98
00:04:48,802 --> 00:04:51,821
对，他是我弟弟
Yeah.He's my brother.

99
00:04:53,990 --> 00:04:58,294
合金钢管，橡胶雷管
Galvanized-metal pipe.Rubber blasting caps.

100
00:04:58,328 --> 00:05:00,362
把钳子递给我
Hand me those pliers.

101
00:05:00,380 --> 00:05:03,249
好的
All right.

102
00:05:13,260 --> 00:05:14,260
老康，可能是短的那根
Tino,there could be a short.

103
00:05:14,311 --> 00:05:17,012
嘘，别说话
Shh. Quiet.

104
00:05:36,116 --> 00:05:39,452
现在我们要做的
Now all we got to do...

105
00:05:40,837 --> 00:05:43,556
就是找出是谁要杀我
...Is figure out who's trying to kill me.

106
00:05:51,047 --> 00:05:53,299
炸弹解除了
It's disarmed.

107
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:55,601
谢天谢地
thank God.

108
00:05:55,635 --> 00:05:57,603
那么，到底谁想杀你？
So,who wants you dead?

109
00:05:57,637 --> 00:05:59,922
现在？猜猜看
Nowadays? Pick a number.

110
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:04,927
我手下的姑娘认识一个炸弹专家
One of my girls has a regular on the bomb squad.

111
00:06:04,945 --> 00:06:07,029
我可以找他帮忙
I could ask him to take a look at the device,

112
00:06:07,063 --> 00:06:08,697
没准能找出是谁送的炸弹
Maybe help us figure out who sent it.

113
00:06:08,732 --> 00:06:10,032
那，你觉得你找的这个人
Well, do you think you can trust this guy

114
00:06:10,066 --> 00:06:11,317
能保守秘密吗？
To keep his mouth shut?

115
00:06:11,368 --> 00:06:14,120
我手里有他的把柄
I have a video of him in a compromising position.

116
00:06:14,154 --> 00:06:15,121
好吧
Yeah.

117
00:06:15,155 --> 00:06:17,289
你让他动作快一点
Well, you tell him to work quick.

118
00:06:17,324 --> 00:06:20,609
因为甭管是谁送的炸弹，他还会再有新的行动
Because whoever did this --they're gonna try again.

119
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:25,240
Subtitle by @godort

120
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:30,200
《黑帮天使》第一季 第11集 “手足相残”
The Mob Doctor Season 1, Episode 11, "Sibling Rivalry"

121
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,800
汉森先生，握我的手
Mr. Hanson, squeeze my hand!

122
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,641
没反应
Non-responsive.

123
00:06:36,659 --> 00:06:38,976
如果杰克・汉森是你弟弟，那马克・汉森就是……
If Jack Hanson is your brother,then Mark Hanson --

124
00:06:38,994 --> 00:06:40,811
就是我爸爸
Is my father.

125
00:06:40,829 --> 00:06:42,530
*******我只是退出了痛苦的刺激
Only withdraws to painful stimuli.

126
00:06:42,581 --> 00:06:45,250
你们不同姓？
Different last name?

127
00:06:45,284 --> 00:06:47,919
随我妈的姓，我在上大学的时候改的
It's my mother's maiden name.I changed it during college.

128
00:06:47,953 --> 00:06:49,837
咱待会再说这个行么？
Can we talk about this later?

129
00:06:49,872 --> 00:06:51,873
放一思达清理肾功能
Run an I-stat to clear his renal function,

130
00:06:51,924 --> 00:06:53,758
先给他扫描
Then pan-scan him --priority one.

131
00:06:53,792 --> 00:06:54,360
苏西说的对
Susie is right.

132
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:56,094
我得把他推到放射科去
I'll roll him to radiology.

133
00:06:56,128 --> 00:06:57,262
不行，病人家属不能参与治疗
No, he's a family member.

134
00:06:57,296 --> 00:07:00,431
你可以看着，但从现在开始不能插手
You can observe.But from here on, hands off.

135
00:07:00,466 --> 00:07:02,500
德芙琳大夫，你的VIP病人怎么样了？
Dr. Devlin,how's your V.I.P. Patient?

136
00:07:02,518 --> 00:07:03,685
他没有生命危险
His vitals are stable.

137
00:07:03,719 --> 00:07:05,836
很好，我需要你参加一个外科会诊
Good. I need you for a surgical consult.

138
00:07:05,854 --> 00:07:07,305
走吧
Let's go.

139
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,725
药的副作用
Bounce-back，lower-right quadrant pain.

140
00:07:10,776 --> 00:07:13,645
让她右下腹疼痛
Medicine turfed her to us.

141
00:07:16,398 --> 00:07:18,199
开玩笑呢吧
you're joking.

142
00:07:18,233 --> 00:07:20,451
你认识伊文斯夫人？
You already know Ms. Evans?

143
00:07:20,486 --> 00:07:23,020
她经常到这来拿药
She's a frequent flyer.She's here for drugs.

144
00:07:23,038 --> 00:07:24,789
我得提醒你
Let me remind you that you've already received

145
00:07:24,823 --> 00:07:26,574
你已经有两次服务态度差评了，所以
Two failing grades on the patient surveys, so --

146
00:07:26,625 --> 00:07:29,077
弗拉尼根大夫，这只是一个创伤复查
Dr. Flanigan,it was a wound recheck

147
00:07:29,128 --> 00:07:30,878
谁会因为我正做的阑尾切除术急呢
Who got mad that I was busy with a ruptured appy...

148
00:07:30,913 --> 00:07:34,699
大夫，还有给粪便栓塞做直肠检查
Doctor... And a fecal impaction who resented the rectal exam.

149
00:07:34,717 --> 00:07:36,033
大夫
Doctor.

150
00:07:36,051 --> 00:07:37,868
这是她的病例
Her chart is up and loaded.

151
00:07:41,824 --> 00:07:43,725
嘿，伊文斯小姐，我是德芙琳大夫
Hi, Miss Evans. I'm Dr. Devlin.

152
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:47,211
对，我记得你
Yeah. I remember you.

153
00:07:47,229 --> 00:07:48,930
抱歉让你久等了
Sorry you had to wait so long.

154
00:07:48,981 --> 00:07:50,548
我他妈都等了几个小时了
four damn hours.

155
00:07:50,566 --> 00:07:52,233
等死我了
could have died.

156
00:07:54,269 --> 00:07:56,053
那么，你的下腹部疼痛
So, you have pain in your lower abdomen.

157
00:07:56,071 --> 00:07:57,054
对吗？
Is that right?

158
00:07:57,072 --> 00:07:58,222
对，好吧，我看一下
Yeah.Okay, may I?

159
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:01,726
好
Yeah. 

160
00:08:01,744 --> 00:08:03,928
听着，我需要点止疼药
Look, I'm gonna -- I'm gonna need something for the pain.

161
00:08:03,963 --> 00:08:07,949
我对布洛芬，酮类和吗啡过敏
I'm allergic to ibuprofen,ketorolac, and morphine.

162
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,283
嗯
Mm.

163
00:08:09,335 --> 00:08:11,953
有一种D打头的药
There's this other drug,"d"-something.

164
00:08:12,004 --> 00:08:13,287
盐酸氢吗啡酮？
Dilaudid?

165
00:08:13,322 --> 00:08:15,006
对，对
Yeah.Yeah.

166
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:17,792
你的病征有点轻微扩散
You have mild,diffuse tenderness.

167
00:08:17,843 --> 00:08:20,011
没有反弹，没有保护
No rebound, no guarding.

168
00:08:20,045 --> 00:08:22,463
股动脉很正常
Strong femoral pulses.

169
00:08:22,514 --> 00:08:24,298
是啊，这真是好消息
Yeah, this is really all good news.

170
00:08:24,350 --> 00:08:27,268
你聋了吗？
Are -- are you deaf?

171
00:08:27,302 --> 00:08:30,304
我刚才说很疼
I -- I said it hurts.

172
00:08:30,356 --> 00:08:33,474
你知道你们医院的规定吗？
Are you familiar with your own hospital's policy?

173
00:08:33,525 --> 00:08:35,443
你说什么？听着
Excuse me? Look. 

174
00:08:35,477 --> 00:08:36,611
你得给我做个CT
You need to order me a C.T.,

175
00:08:36,645 --> 00:08:38,479
还得给我拿点止疼药
And the you need to get me something for the pain.

176
00:08:38,530 --> 00:08:39,764
行了，伊文斯小姐，你每年到医院来八十一次
Okay, Miss Evans,you've actually been here

177
00:08:39,782 --> 00:08:43,151
每次都有新的病征
81 times this year,each time with a new complaint.

178
