Um, I'm waiting on some test results. What's going on?

189
00:09:17,436 --> 00:09:19,137
求你了，这事很严重，你必须过来一趟
Please, it's important.You got to get over here.

190
00:09:19,171 --> 00:09:20,971
那好吧
Okay, fine.

191
00:09:20,989 --> 00:09:22,807
哦，我时间不多
Uh, I just don't have much time, though.

192
00:09:22,825 --> 00:09:25,142
我把地址发给你
I'm texting you the address.

193
00:09:33,318 --> 00:09:35,286
咱们得快点
We got to hurry.

194
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,622
为什么叫我到这儿来好吗？我把事情搞砸了，
Tell me why I'm here, Nate.I screwed up, okay?

195
00:09:37,656 --> 00:09:39,290
我知道上回说不让你帮忙了，可是这回我需要你
I-I know what I said before,but I need your help.

196
00:09:39,324 --> 00:09:40,792
跟我来好吗？
Just follow me, okay?

197
00:09:40,826 --> 00:09:42,993
要是有紧急情况，你就应该报警
If you have an emergency,you call 911.

198
00:09:43,011 --> 00:09:44,879
除了你我谁也不能告诉
I can't call anybody except you!

199
00:09:44,930 --> 00:09:45,880
为什么
Why not?

200
00:09:45,931 --> 00:09:50,051
格蕾丝
Grace...

201
00:09:50,102 --> 00:09:52,386
来见见马蒂小子
Meet Matty Boy.

202
00:09:52,421 --> 00:09:54,539
马
A horse.

203
00:09:54,573 --> 00:09:55,857
纯种赛马
Thoroughbred racehorse.

204
00:09:55,891 --> 00:09:57,191
