No, a vet would call the cops.

206
00:09:59,278 --> 00:10:01,212
你是谁？
Who are you?

207
00:10:01,246 --> 00:10:03,364
格蕾丝，这是维克多
Grace, Victor.

208
00:10:03,398 --> 00:10:05,700
为什么不能让警察知道？
Call the cops for what?

209
00:10:05,734 --> 00:10:08,236
这不是我们的马
It's not our horse.

210
00:10:08,287 --> 00:10:11,739
马蒂小子赢过阿灵顿比赛
Matty Boy won the Arlington Cup.

211
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:15,359
他的精子价值十万美元
His sperm is worth 100 grand.

212
00:10:15,377 --> 00:10:17,829
精子？
His sperm?

213
00:10:31,393 --> 00:10:33,377
他怎么勃起了？
Why does he have an erection?

214
00:10:33,395 --> 00:10:35,930
