And now it won't go down.

219
00:10:44,723 --> 00:10:46,824
这马明天还有一场比赛
The horse has got to race tomorrow.

220
00:10:46,859 --> 00:10:48,826
我得走了
Yeah, I got to go.

221
00:10:48,861 --> 00:10:50,444
求你了，格蕾丝
Grace, please.

222
00:10:50,496 --> 00:10:53,781
有患者需要我，内特，人类患者
I have patients who need me, Nate -- people patients.

223
00:10:53,832 --> 00:10:56,734
